Overview:






Screens:

# main page (index.html):
- Path in site: Loads when loading the site.
                While navigating in other pages there is a house icon on the top left corner. When clicked you will be navigated back to this page.

- Features:     
The first three features are provided by the autocomplete dropdown search box.
1. Search for a movie
2. Search for an actor
3. Search for a catagory

Each of those searches provides the option to click on the 'Search' button, to see all the results with the corresponding title (/ name) (meaning that the
title (/ name) includes the searched text)

4. Genres cloud - By clicking on the button 'Show Me A Cloud', a cloud of genre names will appear, where the text size of the names is descending by the
number of actors who play in that genre.